snippet.title: Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater (PS3) - Shagohod Boss Batle Gameplay Playthrough (Part 28)
snippet.description:
Snake  and Eva fighting agains Volgin and his Shagohod.

This video is part of my playthrough playing Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater HD Edition, third game in the Metal Gear "Solid" saga, dubbed and subtitled in English and no commentary.
I've also done playthroughs of the MSX versions re-released on PS3 and MGS1 and MGS2, check my playlists!

Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater was a game originally released for Playstation 2 (PS2).

Release data:
Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater HD Edition (2011) / Included in Metal Gear Solid: The Legacy Collection (2013)
Genre: Action / Stealth
Platform: Playstation 3 (PS3) 
Developer: KCEJ, Bluepoint Games
Publisher: Konami

Complete Playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nad2QT8OJ6M&list=PL_YL558gxlL9-I1vzJD9ecSUlO5CCEB5k

Recorded at 60 fps with Live Gamer Portable 2 - GC510.

#metalgearsolid3 #mgs3 #snakeeater
